  <name>Snickerstream</name>
  <summary>Nintendo 3DS Streaming Client</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Snickerstream is a powerful streaming client for Nintendo 3DS consoles that supports both NTR and HzMod streaming methods. 
      It offers real-time screen scaling, multiple interpolation modes, various screen layouts, and many customizable features 
      for an optimal 3DS streaming experience.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support for both NTR CFW and HzMod streaming</li>
      <li>Real-time screen scaling and interpolation</li>
      <li>Multiple screen layouts including fullscreen modes</li>
      <li>Built-in screenshot functionality</li>
      <li>Automatic remoteplay initialization</li>
      <li>Customizable hotkeys</li>
      <li>Multiple console streaming support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
